data.name: Rickroll
data.description:
# Rickroll

Write a function that returns an iterator creating the next word in the chorus of Rick Astley's Never Gonna Give You Up.

For the purpose of this Kata, use the following lyrics
```
Never gonna give you up
Never gonna let you down
Never gonna run around and desert you
Never gonna make you cry
Never gonna say goodbye
Never gonna tell a lie and hurt you
```

For example, when called five times your function should return:
```
rickroll() // "Never"
rickroll() // "gonna"
rickroll() // "give"
rickroll() // "you"
rickroll() // "up"
```

After the whole text has been returned, it does not matter what the function returns next.
